%% QGX LMS - UML Sequence Diagram (Mermaid)
%% Student test attempt and submission flow with auth, API, DB, and audit logging
sequenceDiagram
    actor Student
    participant UI as Next.js UI
    participant API as API Route
    participant Auth as Supabase Auth
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Supabase)
    participant Log as Activity Logger

    Student->>UI: Open test page
    UI->>API: GET /api/tests/{id}
    API->>Auth: Validate session token
    Auth-->>API: Session valid

    API->>DB: Fetch test and questions
    DB-->>API: Return test payload
    API-->>UI: 200 OK + test data
    UI-->>Student: Render test interface

    Student->>UI: Submit answers
    UI->>API: POST /api/attempts
    API->>Auth: Re-validate session and role
    Auth-->>API: Authorized

    API->>DB: Store attempt and compute score
    DB-->>API: Persisted attempt + score

    API->>Log: Record submission event
    Log-->>API: Log written

    API-->>UI: 201 Created + score
    UI-->>Student: Show result and feedback
